{"tid":864388,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳家駒：香港人權民主法、政策法宜並存","createTime":"2018-10-16T07:19:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-16T09:48:10.000Z","uid":14719,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"dca4bb0a90bdcf84b1541369f247bd8b652d670d","tid":864388,"uid":14719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T07:19:06.000Z","msg":"[獨家] 陳家駒：香港人權民主法、政策法宜並存（曾焯文報導） <br />\n<br />\nExclusive: Pro-independence Student Wayne Chan Thinks HK Human Rights &amp; Democracy Act and HK Policy Act had Better Co-exist (Chapman Chen reports)<br />\n<br />\n學生獨立聯盟陳家駒今朝八點半遞交請願信，予美國領事HARRY先生，請美國通過香港人權民主法案，制裁壓抑同破壞香港民主自由的香港及中國官員。其後接受本報獨家訪問，認為美國通過香港人權民主法機會頗大，事關美國國會及行政當局中國委員會上週發表中國人權報告，措辭強硬，而且美國共和民主兩黨經達成共識，聯手對付中國。<br />\n<br />\n陳家駒又話香港人權民主法案處理政治，香港政策法案處理經濟，兩者宜並存。陳氏不主張取消香港政策法，事關香港人權民主法若通過，已可達到制裁香港及中國官員目的，而香港政策法關乎香港之國際地位，無疑可用以警告中方，<span style=\"color: red;\">然而一旦取消，不但影響香港經濟，而且令外商失去在港利益，從此不會再關心香港民主人權。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.localpresshk.com/2018/10/ka-kui-act/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.localpresshk.com%2F2018%2F10%2Fka-kui-act%2F&d=EhBP80KDfqtSfCVNn%2BWU%2FmMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=0706c317\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.localpresshk.com/2018/10/ka-kui-act/</a>"},{"pid":"f2b3ea5b7f7b363613978de41714a1f4c7d16fe9","tid":864388,"uid":14719,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T07:21:01.000Z","msg":"陳浩天促美廢除香港政策法　美駐港領事：美對港態度不變<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">香港民族黨召集人兩度去信美國總統特朗普和美國國務院，指香港政策背離民主，要求美方取消給予香港特殊待遇的香港政策法。</span>美國駐港總領事唐偉康今日表示，香港現時享有的自主，仍然高於香港政策法的要求，不會影響美國對中國和香港的態度。<br />\n<br />\n唐偉康又表示，今年是美國駐港總領事館成立175周年，美國和香港一直在貿易和其他議題上，保持密切和良好關係。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/陳浩天促美廢除香港政策法-美駐港領事-美對港態度不變/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E9%99%B3%E6%B5%A9%E5%A4%A9%E4%BF%83%E7%BE%8E%E5%BB%A2%E9%99%A4%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%94%BF%E7%AD%96%E6%B3%95-%E7%BE%8E%E9%A7%90%E6%B8%AF%E9%A0%98%E4%BA%8B-%E7%BE%8E%E5%B0%8D%E6%B8%AF%E6%85%8B%E5%BA%A6%E4%B8%8D%E8%AE%8A%2F&d=EhBP80KDfqtSfCVNn%2BWU%2FmMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=0112803e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E9%99%B3%E6%B5%A9%E5%A4%A9%E4%BF%83%E7%BE%8E%E5%BB%A2%E9%99%A4%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%94%BF%E7%AD%96%E6%B3%95-%E7%BE%8E%E9%A7%90%E6%B8%AF%E9%A0%98%E4%BA%8B-%E7%BE%8E%E5%B0%8D%E6%B8%AF%E6%85%8B%E5%BA%A6%E4%B8%8D%E8%AE%8A%2F&h=96195253\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/陳浩天促美廢除香港政策法-美駐港領事-美對港態度不變/</a>"},{"pid":"fe3a550b5b3ae2fba6d302626c511d366d5018c2","tid":864388,"uid":14719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T09:03:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39bd4bb1cb96841687c90694ee2c86972c905c5c","tid":864388,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T09:40:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7708ccd84b16f760c37ecfd54bb3dd199f37720","tid":864388,"uid":33481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T09:48:10.000Z","msg":"屌，你姐係踩鳩至高無上既天哥台姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}